"1\" width=\"100%\" noshade=\"\" align=\"center\">\n\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、美国人玛丽在云南旅游期间住在一农村居民家中，其应当在入住后（<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>）内，由本人或者留宿人向居住地公安机关办理登记。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nA</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>小时<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nB</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>小时<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nC</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">48</span>小时<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nD</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">72</span>小时<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">【正确答案<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>】<span lang=\"EN-US\">B<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">\n\n<hr size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" noshade=\"\" align=\"center\">\n\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、美国人吉尔在朋友李某家中住宿，须于入住后（）内，向居住地公安机关办理登记。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nA.8</span>小时<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;B.12</span>小时<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\nC.24</span>小时<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;D.48</span>小时<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">【正确答案<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>】<span lang=\"EN-US\">C<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">\n\n<hr size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" noshade=\"\" align=\"center\">\n\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、下列有关外国人管理的说法不正确的是（<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nA</span>．甲餐厅聘用一名韩国学生做服务员，该餐厅应当向所在地公安机关报告<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">B</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．在中国停留的汤姆和玛丽生了一名男孩，他们应当向停留地公安机关报告<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">C</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">．李某发现某家教公司有外国人非法就业，他应当及时向公安机关报告<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nD</span>．非洲人鲁图在中国死亡，其家属或代理人应当立即向其所在地民政部门报告，并到公安机关注销其出入境证件<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">【正确答案<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>】<span lang=\"EN-US\">D<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">\n\n<hr size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" noshade=\"\" align=\"center\">\n\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">5</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、对下列非法入境的外国人，可以适用拘留审查的有（<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>）。<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\nA</span>．怀孕的朝鲜妇女<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\nB</span>．哺乳自己不满<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>周岁婴儿的越南妇女<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nC</span>．患有严重心脏病的尼日利亚人<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nD</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">65</span>周岁的利比亚人<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">【正确答案<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>】<span lang=\"EN-US\">D<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\n宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">\n\n<hr size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" noshade=\"\" align=\"center\">\n\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、外国人被遣送出境的，自被遣送出境之日起（<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span>）内不准入境。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nA</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nB</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nC</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span>至<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nD</span>．<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">【正确答案<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>】<span lang=\"EN-US\">A<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:\n0pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><div class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">\n\n<hr size=\"1\" width=\"100%\" noshade=\"\" align=\"center\">\n\n</span></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt\">、美国人汤姆非法入境，其对公安机关限制活动范围措施不服，（）。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nA.</span>可以向人民法院提起行政诉讼<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nB.</span>可以依法申请行政复议，该行政复议决定为最终决定<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br>\nC.</span>对行政复议决定不服，方可再提起行政诉讼<span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>\nD.</span>限制活动范围决定为最终决定，不能申请行政复议也不能提起行政诉讼<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><b><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\nmso-font-kerning:0pt\">【正确答案<span lang=\"EN-US\">:</span>】<span lang=\"EN-US\">B<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-fon