INSERT INTO `test_self` VALUES ('TS4844ca2d4d2941bba28ab85e6fa00ce6', '出入境管理法', '基本级', '执法资格等级考试', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b><u><spanyes\';font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><font face=\"宋体\">出入境管理法</font></spanyes\';font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></u></b><b><u><spanyes\';font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></spanyes\';font-family:ˎ̥;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:16.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">1、韩国人朴某非法入境，其对公安机关限制活动范围措施不服，（）。<spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><br><spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">A.可以申请行政复议<spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><br><spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">B.可以向人民法院提起行政诉讼&nbsp;<spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><br><spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">C.可以先申请行政复议再提起行政诉讼&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><br><spanyes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">D.限制活动范围决定为最终决定，不能申请